1.https://github.com/ccny-ros-pkg/ccny_camera_drivers/blob/master/README.md\

2.add the package to rosws(rosws set)

3.download the mvVirtualDevice drivers for the bluefox camera
	http://www.matrix-vision.com/mvvirtualdevice-442.html
	(current one is mvVirtualDevicex86_64_ABI2-2.4.2.tgz
4.get the Makefile from the boat out of fuerte_workspace/ccny_mvVirtualDevice	

4.place the tgz in the ccny_mvVirtualDevice/build folder and type
	md5sum mvVirtualDevicex86_64_ABI2.tgz > ../mvVirtualDevicex86_64_ABI2.tgz.md5sum

5.put this md5sum file in the ccny_mvVirtualDevice directory

6. rosmake ccny_mvVirtualDevice
7. rosmake mv_bluefox_driver

